    <briefdescription>
<para>The constraint function that updates the target property with the value of the first source. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><emphasis>current</emphasis> = <emphasis>input[0]</emphasis>. <emphasis>current</emphasis> and <emphasis>input[0]</emphasis> indicate the target property and the first constraint source (the one added by the first <ref refid="classDali_1_1Constraint_1a8229723a5a2f26afdf4b92ed600c90a8" kindref="member">Constraint::AddSource</ref> call), respectively. @SINCE_1_0.0 </para>
